title: Pet-Friendly, Double Vanity Sinks, Tiled Backsplashes
posting_body: Welcome to Pine Prairie ApartmentsTheres no place like these homes at Pine Prairie Apartments in Lewisville, TX.
Practically built just for you, our one-, two-, and three-bedroom apartments and townhomes come complete with attached garages, stainless steel appliances, and quartz countertops.
As a resident of our community, located near East Hill Park, youll enjoy modern amenities like our swimming pool and fitness center.
If youre looking for a new home, come see why Pine Prairie Apartments is more than a place to live its a lifestyle to love.
